Kungijabulisile ukuthi enyangeni yembokodo ngiyibone iqatha indima ebisihlule amadoda. Kuyaye kuthiwe okuhlula amadoda kuyabikwa kodwa mina ngithi okuhlula amadoda kulungiswa abesifazane. Akumele sibashaye indiva ngemisebenzi abayenzile abaholi abanjengomama uThokozile Xasa wezemidlalo nomama uNomvula Monkanyane wezokuxhumana kodwa kumele babongwe besaphila.Uyazi umkhankaso kaThuma Mina bawusebenzisile ngoba bagxume bahlala ezinkingeni ebezikhungethe abantu abaningi ngokungasakazwa kwemidlalo emisakazweni ye SABC. Kumele sithi nisebenzile bomama besizwe sakithi. Emuva kokuzwa ukuthi iSABC ithi ayivumelani nePSL ngokuthi kusakazwe imidlalo, abantu abangifikele yibo omama uThokozile Xasa nomama uNomvula Nonkonyane ukuthi bathule bathini uma kunje? Okungithokozisile wukuthi bagxume bahlala babiza izikhulu zamadoda ePSL ebeziholwa ubaba * -Irvin Khoza babhunga base bephuma nesisisombululo. Lokho kungikhombisile ukuthi ubuholi besibhuda bunamandla ekulungiseni izinto ngobunono. Kumele sibonge kakhulu kulaba baholi besifazane bese sibanxusa ukuthi balungise inkinga ekuSABC ezoholela ekutheni kulimale indimbane zabantu . Mina nje ngingedwa nginishayela ihlombe bomama ngobuholi benu obunobuchule nobuqotho. Ngiyafisa ukuba nilungise izinkinga zeSABC ngokushesha ukuze kugwemeke izinkinga ezifana nokungasakazwa kwemidlalo ngomuso.  Khabzela “KB” Mzimela EZWELIBOMVU